casebody.data:
Eckhart, Appellant, v. Devine, Respondent. (Common Pleas of New York City and County, General Term. May 5, 1890.) Appeal from eighth district court.

Argued before Larremore, C. J., and Bookstaver, J.

M. K. McCarten, for appellant. Thompson, Ackley & Kauffmann, for respondent.

No opinion. Ordered that the judgment be affirmed, with costs.
